            "title": "高盛執行長所羅門:市場對伊朗戰爭的反應出奇溫和",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高盛執行長所羅門:市場對伊朗戰爭的反應出奇溫和\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0rkSMUFwPS0tULVSZ4TVsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/46e19440-17ee-11f1-9dfb-f349792aef70\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高盛執行長所羅門:市場對伊朗戰爭的反應出奇溫和</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
