            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"伊朗推遲哈梅內伊的葬禮 因預計將出現大規模哀悼人群\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jlgqtfI2HJyA329aSS9dEw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/45aac620-17e7-11f1-bea9-c57f7f588c07\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">伊朗推遲哈梅內伊的葬禮 因預計將出現大規模哀悼人群</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
